These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, guinea-pig, pony
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, dunhill, davidoff, bolivar
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, turquise, white, green
1. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person who likes white is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk   | sprite  | hot-chocolate  |
| Pet   | horse    | pony    | goldfish      | guinea-pig    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | dunhill | davidoff | swisher |
| Color     | green  | orange       | turquise    | white     |

