.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, september, october
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, malaysian, brazilian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, lemonade, 7up
City: marseilles, liverpool, hamburg, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the brazilian is between the person drinking lemonade and the person traveling to marseilles##2
6. the person traveling to boston is between the brazilian and the person drinking 7up##2
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the malaysian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | october | january    | september  | july    |
| Nationality   | colombian      | spanish  | brazilian  | malaysian |
| Beverage           | 7up      | lemonade       | juice      | mirinda       |
| City         | liverpool    | boston | hamburg | marseilles |

