There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pepper, peas, pumpkin
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, cain, aristoff, montecristo
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating pepper##1
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
10. the person drinking milk is between the person eating cauliflower and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | fanta  | coffee | milk     | tea |
| Birthday   | november | january  | june | august       |
| Food           | pepper       | pumpkin    | peas      | cauliflower           |
| Cigar         | dunhill | cain   | montecristo   | aristoff         |

