 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the blend-smoker is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person traveling to paris and the person playing backgammon##2
10. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
