4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, blend, aristoff, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, subway, helicopter
 1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | action    | thriller      | crime |
| Sport       | biathlon        | snowboarding       | skiing       | tennis     |
